<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hun tuibang kiemin muolliem zel,
 Lei thil kumsawt tin umlo;
 Kumsawt thilhaw mai lunggulh in,
 Pathien khut muonum chu tu'n.

[V2]
 Tu'n la, Pathien khut chu tu'n (2)
 Kumsawt thilhaw mai lunggulh in;
 Pathien khut muonum chu tu'n.

[V3]
 2. Hun nungsawn ngeilopa muongin,
 Damsung bang tuok mahleh chin;
 Guol deihte'n hun nusie mahleu,
 Amah naih zaw diekin tu'n.

[V4]
 3. Khawvel neihzawhna awtcha ki'n,
 Kintaka sie'n a bei zel;
 Van go hauhsakna te hawlin,
 Go mang thei ngeilo ahi.

[V5]
 4. Na damsung khuolzin na zawh tieng,
 Pathien di'n na ginum chun;
 Van In nuom lopi leh vak chuh,
 Na tha'n nuomsan luoh ina.</lyrics>
<title>HOLD TO GOD'S UNCHANGING HAND</title>
</song>